Privacy Policy
We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy applies to the APP and controls data collection and usage.
1. Application permissions:
In order to provide our services, we need access to certain permissions on your device, including:
Microphone: To enable speech-to-text translation, we need access to your device's microphone. This is necessary to capture and process your voice input.
Photo Library: We need access to your device's photo library so that you can select images for translation or other purposes.
2. Data collection:
We do not collect any personal information from you, such as name, email address or any other personally identifiable information. We only collect non-personal information, including non-sensitive information such as device ID, system version, system language and country or region. This information is used to improve our services and provide a better user experience.
3. Share information
We do not share any personal information with any third parties. Aggregated, non-personal information such as device IDs, advertising identifiers, etc. may only be shared with partners to help improve our services.
4. Retention of information
We will retain the information collected for as long as you use our services. When you stop using our services, we will delete any remaining information.
5.. Update privacy policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes to our practices or services. We will notify you of any material changes by posting a notice on our App or other reasonable means.
6. Contact us
If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy or data collection practices, you can contact us through our official email or other reasonable means.